# Documentation Sync Rule

**CRITICAL**: Every time you make a functional change to the plugin, you MUST update the relevant documentation.

## What Counts as a Functional Change?

- New features or capabilities added
- Existing features modified or removed
- New settings or configuration options
- Changes to user-facing behavior
- New commands or UI elements
- Changes to data structures that affect user experience
- Performance improvements that users should know about
- Breaking changes or migrations

## Documentation That Must Be Updated

### 1. Feature Documentation (`docs/features/`)

**When to update**: Adding/modifying features

**Files to check**:
- `docs/features/participants.md` - Participant note features
- `docs/features/entity-extraction.md` - Entity extraction (Pro)
- `docs/features/auto-linking.md` - Auto-linking behavior
- `docs/features/import.md` - Import functionality
- `docs/features/otter-sync.md` - Otter.ai integration
- `docs/features/fireflies.md` - Fireflies.ai integration
- `docs/features/folder-watcher.md` - Folder watching
- `docs/features/dashboard.md` - Dashboard features

**What to update**:
- Feature descriptions
- How it works sections
- Configuration options
- Examples and screenshots
- Limitations or caveats

### 2. User Guide (`docs/guide/`)

**When to update**: Changes affecting user workflows

**Files to check**:
- `docs/guide/getting-started.md` - First-time user experience
- `docs/guide/quick-start.md` - Quick setup guide
- `docs/guide/settings.md` - Settings documentation
- `docs/guide/output.md` - Output format and structure
- `docs/guide/sources.md` - Transcript sources

**What to update**:
- Step-by-step instructions
- Settings descriptions and defaults
- Output examples
- Workflow changes

### 3. Pro Features (`docs/pro/`)

**When to update**: Changes to Pro-only features

**Files to check**:
- `docs/pro/overview.md` - Pro feature list
- `docs/pro/participant-insights.md` - Participant insights
- `docs/pro/entity-extraction.md` - Entity extraction
- `docs/pro/action-items.md` - Action items
- `docs/pro/decisions.md` - Decision tracking
