### 4. Landing Page (`frontend/`)

**When to update**: Major feature additions or changes to core value proposition

**Files to check**:
- `frontend/App.tsx` - Main landing page content
- `frontend/metadata.json` - Site metadata and description

**What to update**:
- Feature highlights
- Screenshots or demos
- Value propositions
- Call-to-action text

**Example sections in App.tsx**:
