### 5. Demo Scripts (`docs/demos/`)

**When to update**: Changes that affect demo workflows

**Files to check**:
- `docs/demos/DEMO-SCRIPT.md` - Main demo script
- `docs/demos/DEMO-SCRIPT-MARKETING-REVIEW.md` - Marketing demo

**What to update**:
